lf-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>79.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$279.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $200.01</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/07mLSb989GPj1IhSAOSLz4Q/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1722884570.jpg" alt="Simple Way 宠物美容吸尘器，6 合 1 狗美容套件，具有 3 种吸力模式和大容量尘杯，用于脱毛美容的狗吸尘器和家用狗毛宠物吸尘器（白色）" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/07mLSb989GPj1IhSAOSLz4Q/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1722884570.jpg" alt="Simple Way 宠物美容吸尘器，6 合 1 狗美容套件，具有 3 种吸力模式和大容量尘杯，用于脱毛美容的狗吸尘器和家用狗毛宠物吸尘器（白色）" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">获得优惠</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>79.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$279.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $200.01</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>根据您宠物的美容需求，真空吸尘器有许多不同的附件。如果他们的头发太长，有一个剃须刀附件（带有几个不同尺寸的护罩）可以在切割时吸收所有剃过的头发。 （请记住<a href="https://www.akc.org/expert-advice/health/is-it-ok-to-shave-your-dog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">，根据 AKC 的说法</a>，根据狗狗的品种，给狗狗剃毛可能不是一个好主意。在使用剪刀之前，请先做一些研究，了解最适合您宠物的方法。）还有一个除毛刷用于更多日常梳理的附件，以及更简单的真空附件，用于吸走第一次错过的任何东西。</p><p>由于<a href="https://lifehacker.com/how-to-groom-your-dog-at-home-without-traumatizing-them-1847867963" target="_blank">宠物在吸尘器周围往往会感到不安</a>，Simple Way 声称它的运行噪音为 75 分贝， <a href="https://mgaleg.maryland.gov/cmte_testimony/2024/ecm/1I7X18LiLthdHKhxoqw3LAFT_0-LwKMXh.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">大约与淋浴、洗碗机或搅拌机的噪音一样</a>。对我来说，这听起来并不比普通真空吸尘器安静得多，但我认为任何噪音的减少都是有帮助的。不管怎样， <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4r09IEapD18" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">YouTube 上的</a>这位评论者表明，他的（非常可爱的）金毛猎犬似乎并没有受到真空吸尘器声音的影响。当然，金毛猎犬往往不会被大多数事情所困扰。你的旅费可能会改变。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/family/pet-grooming-vacuum-sale<dc:creator>普拉德希卡·夏尔马</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Pets]]></category></item><item><title>我今天最喜欢的亚马逊优惠：iPad Mini</title><guid ispermalink="false"> 01J4J0GC3NA86EK91KPKB41CXZ</guid><pubDate> Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:30:00 +0000</pubDate><description>第六代 iPad mini 在享受 120 美元折扣后又恢复至 Prime Day 价格。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J4J0GC3NA86EK91KPKB41CXZ/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>第 6